description:
In Response to Trader Inquiry: A livestream does not count for this market - individual songs must be streamable and replayable on the website outside of a livestream. 

This is a market on whether Donda 2 will be available for stream or download on stemplayer.com, as advertised on the official Kanye West instagram (https://www.instagram.com/p/CaHAZv4ju7N/) on February 22, 2022, PT. If Donda 2 can be streamed or downloaded from stemplayer.com at any point on February 22, 2022, PT, this market will resolve to "Yes". Otherwise this market will resolve to "No".

The market resolution source is stemplayer.com. Whether Donda 2 can be streamed or downloaded on other platforms or from other URLs will have no impact on the settlement of this market. If the specified website is unavailable for the entirety of the resolution date this market will resolve to "No".
